name: DAISY
description: Sometimes in life, you have to work hard for what you want. Other times, life gives you something you were not expecting, something you didn't work for, to see if you will work hard to keep it. Whatever the case may be, you won't liquidate life for all its worth until you learn to enjoy the work it takes to reach the final goal. So take your time, enjoy what you have and what you are given, and smile.
